snippet.title: Amber Heard tan-inah a tang thut thei ||Johnny Depp nen an thubuai
snippet.description:
Amber Heard leh Johnny Depp te 2016 a an inthen khan Amber hian khawvel maktih em em mai turin a pasal hlui hian amah sawisa thinah leh tawngkam chhe tak tak hmanga ankhum thinah a puh. Khata tang khan tun thleng hian an inkar boruak a buai zual tulh tulh mai a, hetih karah hian Amber zawk hi tanin a lut maithei dinhmunah a dingmek. International Business Times, April 2020 in a report danin Aquaman changtunu hi a pasal hlui a puhna evidence ama duhdanin a lo siamrem anih chuan kum thum chhung taninah a tan phah thei dawn ani
